item.title: Invailed pass or user?
item.dc:creator: @m_jon_h m jon h
item.description:
@m_jon_h wrote:

Javacisnotrecognized:

You can’t do that if someone else has already claimed that name. By ‘any username or pass’ it means that the server will autoregister you if the account doesn’t exist.

yep so try a different name and if that doesnt work restart moparscape and if that doesnt work ask the owner to restart the server and if that doesnt work your stuffed :o
